Network Interface Process (ENI)

1. select private instance and go to Networking and scroll down find Network Interface and select that ENI and Go to Actions and change
   termination behaviour --> If Enable then  disable it.

2. Terminate the instance and create new instance select vpc and subnet, In additonal configuration select Network Interface and select eni
   create instance.

3. After successfully instance creation check the private IP it will be same.

4. We can also create new ENI Go to Network Interface and create new ENI --> select VPC, subnet, and we can also create custom IP.

5. Attach the newly created ENI to any server and check new IP is also added to the server.
